{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"filter","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/filter","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>«&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>属性<code>filter</code>定义了由<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a>元素定义滤镜效果，该滤镜效果将应用到该元素上。</p>\n\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性。请阅读<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/filter\"><code>css&nbsp;filter</code></a>以了解更多信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#funciri\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#FuncIRI\">&lt;funciri&gt;</a>&nbsp;| <strong>none</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#FilterProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"funciri\"><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#funciri\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#FuncIRI\">&lt;funciri&gt;</a></dt>\n <dd>元素的引用，它定义了将要应用到该元素的滤镜效果。</dd>\n <dt id=\"none\">none</dt>\n <dd>不对该元素应用任何滤镜效果。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>filter</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#graphics_elements\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Graphics_elements\">图形元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/defs\"><code>&lt;defs&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/filter\"><code>css filter</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"filter","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/filter","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/filter/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/filter","title":"filter"}],"pageTitle":"filter - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}